    rdfs:label "emmo-futuram-bridge" ;
    rdfs:comment "FutuRaM -> EMMO alignment: the futuram roots (Product/Material/Element) and futuram:refersTo aligned under their EMMO parents. Moved out of composition-statement.ttl." .

